1089
01:34:08,273 --> 01:34:11,026
<i>We all wake to the human condition.</i>

1090
01:34:11,067 --> 01:34:14,487
<i>We wake to mystery and beauty,</i>

1091
01:34:14,571 --> 01:34:17,699
