1096
01:34:33,173 --> 01:34:35,550
<i>to write love on her arms.</i>

1097
01:34:35,592 --> 01:34:37,427
<i>Rescue is possible.</i>

1098
01:34:37,761 --> 01:34:39,929
<i>God is still in the business of redemption.</i>

1099
01:34:41,681 --> 01:34:45,226
