is the hardest to take.</i>

1100
01:34:45,977 --> 01:34:47,729
<i>But it's worth it.</i>

1101
01:34:48,521 --> 01:34:51,066
<i>Life is worth fighting for.</i>

1102
01:35:05,580 --> 01:35:09,959
Hi, I'm Jamie Tworkowski,
founder of To Write Love on Her Arms.

1103
01:35:10,043 --> 01:35:11,443
Millions of people around the world

1104
01:35:11,461 --> 01:35:15,215
struggle with depression, addiction,
self-injury and suicide.

